com.tombarrasso.android.wp7ui.extras
Class Changelog

java.lang.Object
  com.tombarrasso.android.wp7ui.extras.Changelog

public final class Changelog
extends java.lang.Object

To use this class 4 resources are required:

  • R.raw.changelog: a changelog.txt file stored in the raw diretory of your application.
  • R.string.changelog_title_full: the title to be used in a full screen change log.
  • R.string.changelog_title: the title to be used in a non-full screen change log.
  • R.string.changelog_ok: the text to display on the single button used to dismiss the change log.

public java.lang.String getLastVersion()

The version name of the last installation of this app (as described in the former manifest). This will be the same as returned by getThisVersion() from the second time this version of the app is launched (more precisely: the second time ChangeLog is instantiated).
